plot: Rather than face his writers block and frustration from failed attempts at romance, Josh searches for motivation at the bottom of a beer bottle, at an East Village dive bar.::Murray Wasylnuk

"_One More_ (qv)" is the story of Josh, an uninspired New York writer that spends many days at his local bar, searching for motivation at the bottom of a beer glass with his best pal Graeme. Until one day, inspiration crosses his path in the form of a beautiful muse.::Murray Wasylnuk

ONE MORE is the story of Josh, a New York writer fearful his anxieties will seize control of him as he faces an impending deadline, but choosing to spend his days with his best pal Graeme, searching for inspiration at the bottom of a beer bottle. Until one day, motivation crosses his path in the form of a beautiful muse.
